 20 days.","Check canned foods for water."],"type":"ul"},"id":"01a3cfa5-34c6-4ba8-9035-0814595d37c4","type":"list"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["These are initial resources to help keep you and your family hydrated. But should the crisis progress, there are a few other ways in which to fulfill your hydration needs. Check the news for sources for fresh water. If you don&#39;t have any power, use an <a href=\"/best-crank-radios\">emergency crank radio</a> for updates.","<strong>Seek Moving Water</strong><br/>Moving water is normally much cleaner than the water in a stagnant pool. Moving water has been washing over rocks and other natural forms of water purifiers. You will still have to boil it, though, especially after a rain. When it rains, all the animal waste is pushed through the ground into moving streams. The good news is that after a rain, you should be able to find more sources of water as the groundwater seeks lower elevations."]},"id":"81c7d697-c8e5-4d07-bd03-5745d6d6b849","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/nwSXuzo69GVmoZPDSDqM2N.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/misc/articles/7021/alternate-sourc-2.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwSXuzo69GVmoZPDSDqM2N.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"nwSXuzo69GVmoZPDSDqM2N","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwSXuzo69GVmoZPDSDqM2N.jpg","alt":""},"id":"9453d407-298e-4ffa-9e6e-ea7984e513c2","type":"image"},{"data":{"path":"/EtYsJDVqELidxCuw2M4MXA.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/misc/articles/7021/alternate-sourc-3.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/EtYsJDVqELidxCuw2M4MXA.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"EtYsJDVqELidxCuw2M4MXA","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/EtYsJDVqELidxCuw2M4MXA.jpg","alt":""},"id":"ca71021d-2b2a-4a86-9764-4a6d194f6d3f","type":"image"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_7021","url":"/a